  <brief_title>Modified Atkins Diet and Type 2 Diabetic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influende of a Modified Atkins Diet on Glucose Metabolism and Weight Loss in Obese Type 2 Diabetic Patients - A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
